Class ElementContainer

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.tree.GNode
      • model.ElementContainer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GObservable, java.io.Serializable, javax.swing.tree.MutableTreeNode, javax.swing.tree.TreeNode
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Element, Slot

    public class ElementContainer
extends GNode
implements java.io.Serializable
    Abstract element container. Element containers can have elements as children. Slot and Element are element containers.
    Author:
    geomaster
